  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nBenchmarking validator endpoints in the beacon API, noticed that the proposer duties endpoint (`/eth/v1/validator/duties/proposer/{epoch}`) is significantly slower on lighthouse compared to other nodes\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nLighthouse/v4.1.0-693886b/x86_64-linux\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nSlow response (100s)\r\n\r\nI do see that other nodes (e.g. nimbus) also return a slower response (~20s) possibly until a cache is populated, but lighthouse is consistently slow.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nFaster response, comparable to other consensus nodes (~1s)\r\n",
